      "MedicationRequest?code=http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|42375,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|83008,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1307298,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|1100072,http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/rxnorm|475230",
